---
// Portfolio Section - Humble but Confident Tone
---

<section id="portfolio" class="py-24 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-dark mb-4 tracking-tight">
                Projects I'm Proud Of
            </h2>
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-600">
                A look at some of the complex problems I've had the opportunity to solve recently. From enterprise data systems to creative digital strategies.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
            
            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                <div class="aspect-video bg-gray-100 w-full relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center border-b border-gray-100">
                    <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium">Dashboard UI Image Placeholder</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="p-8">
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary bg-blue-50 rounded-full">Laravel 11</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 rounded-full">Next.js</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 rounded-full">Custom Parsers</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        Global Aquatics Management System
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Developed a highly scalable athletic management platform for a client in Thailand. It handles complex FINA standard data (.lef) and live event results seamlessly using a robust headless architecture.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-semibold hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors">
                        View Case Study 
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="group relative bg-white rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 shadow-sm hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
                <div class="aspect-video bg-gray-100 w-full relative overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center border-b border-gray-100">
                    <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium">Brand/Strategy Image Placeholder</span>
                </div>
                
                <div class="p-8">
                    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-4">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-primary bg-blue-50 rounded-full">UI/UX Design</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 rounded-full">Brand Identity</span>
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 bg-gray-100 rounded-full">Digital Strategy</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-dark mb-3 group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">
                        Digital Growth & Brand Experience
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Helped local businesses find their unique voice and reach their target audience. This ongoing work involves crafting data-driven content, video production, and designing cohesive brand identities.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary font-semibold hover:text-blue-700 transition-colors">
                        View Case Study 
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"/></svg>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</section>